text: Élancourt is a French commune. It is in the western suburbs of Paris, from the center. 25,575 people lived here in 2018. == Twin towns == Élancourt is twinned with: * Laubach, Germany * Cassina de' Pecchi, Italy * Gräfenhainichen, Germany * Attard, Malta Category:Communes in Yvelines
title: Élancourt
